---
title: Shrimp Penne al Limone with Zucchini, Toasted Garlic & Fresh Parsley
description: When life gives you lemons... you could make lemonade. But wouldn’t you rather whip up a delectable homemade pasta limone? This rich, tangy, oh-so-easy sauce comes together in a flash with lemon zest and juice, Parmesan, and butter—plus toasted garlic and a cream sauce base for good measure. It’s all tossed with penne pasta, sautéed zucchini, and chicken breast strips, then garnished with fresh parsley and more Parm. Each bowl’s served with lemon wedges for squeezing on a little extra zing. This dish is truly the best of the zest.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63853599929fb724f40ed140-e3d4003e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65833fab3069c2ab3a848dfe.pdf
author: HelloFresh
time required: 20 minutes
cuisine: Italian
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/shrimp-penne-al-limone-65833fab3069c2ab3a848dfe
servings: 2
course: main course
